   474→%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
   475→%                                                                             %
   476→%                                                                             %
   477→%                                                                             %
   478→%   G e t D e l e g a t e C o m m a n d                                       %
